  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02880', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-098-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '地下層供「各類場所消防安全設備設置標準」之甲類場所使用者，當使用瓦斯時，其樓地板面積合計達 多少平方公尺以上時應設置瓦斯漏氣火警自動警報設備？', '["500平方公尺", "1000平方公尺", "1500平方公尺", "2000平方公尺"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a64d4d092471", "answer_pdf_sha1": "465b7400ec13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098220", "c": "902", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年建築師、技師、消防設備師、不動產經紀人、記帳士、第二次消防設備士、語言治療師", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02881', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-098-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依「各類場所消防安全設備設置標準」規定，建築物高度超過60公尺者，連結送水管應採用濕式，對於 中繼幫浦之規定何者正確？', '["出水量在每分鐘2400公升以上", "中繼幫浦二次側設出水口、止水閥及壓力調整閥，並附設旁通管", "中繼水箱容量為5立方公尺以上", "全閉揚程與押入揚程合計在150公尺以上時，增設幫浦使並聯運轉"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a64d4d092471", "answer_pdf_sha1": "465b7400ec13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098220", "c": "902", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年建築師、技師、消防設備師、不動產經紀人、記帳士、第二次消防設備士、語言治療師", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02882', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-098-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '應設置消防安全設備之場所若未依規定設置消防設備，於發生火災致人於重傷時，應如何處罰其管理權 人？', '["一年以上七年以下有期徒刑", "五十萬元以下之罰鍰", "六月以上五年以下有期徒刑，得併科新臺幣五十萬元以上二百五十萬元以下罰金", "三年以下有期徒刑或拘役，得併科新臺幣二十萬元以上一百萬元以下罰金"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a64d4d092471", "answer_pdf_sha1": "465b7400ec13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098220", "c": "902", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年建築師、技師、消防設備師、不動產經紀人、記帳士、第二次消防設備士、語言治療師", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02883', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-098-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '受信總機、中繼器及偵煙式探測器，有設定蓄積時間時，其蓄積時間之合計，每一火警分區在幾秒以下？', '["20", "30", "60", "90"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a64d4d092471", "answer_pdf_sha1": "465b7400ec13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098220", "c": "902", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年建築師、技師、消防設備師、不動產經紀人、記帳士、第二次消防設備士、語言治療師", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02884', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-098-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依「各類場所消防安全設備設置標準」規定，偵煙式探測器之裝置位置限制於排氣口或回風口周圍多少 距離範圍內？', '["0.5公尺", "1.0公尺", "1.5公尺", "2.0公尺"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a64d4d092471", "answer_pdf_sha1": "465b7400ec13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098220", "c": "902", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年建築師、技師、消防設備師、不動產經紀人、記帳士、第二次消防設備士、語言治療師", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02885', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-098-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依「各類場所消防安全設備設置標準」規定，戲院、電影院等場所天花板及室內牆面如以耐燃一級材料裝 修，而觀眾席天花板高度超出某一高度以上，即可免受「每五百平方公尺內設置防煙壁區劃」之限制。請 問該高度值為何？', '["3公尺", "4公尺", "5公尺", "6公尺"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a64d4d092471", "answer_pdf_sha1": "465b7400ec13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098220", "c": "902", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年建築師、技師、消防設備師、不動產經紀人、記帳士、第二次消防設備士、語言治療師", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02886', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-098-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者非「公共危險物品及可燃性高壓氣體設置標準暨安全管理辦法」所稱可燃性高壓氣體？', '["甲烷、乙烷", "氯氣、乙烯", "乙炔、氫氣", "丙烷、丁烷"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a64d4d092471", "answer_pdf_sha1": "465b7400ec13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098220", "c": "902", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年建築師、技師、消防設備師、不動產經紀人、記帳士、第二次消防設備士、語言治療師", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02887', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-098-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '差動式分布型（空氣管式）檢修時，可以預測空氣管長度是下列那一種試驗？', '["流通試驗", "接點水高試驗", "動作試驗", "持續動作試驗"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a64d4d092471", "answer_pdf_sha1": "465b7400ec13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098220", "c": "902", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年建築師、技師、消防設備師、不動產經紀人、記帳士、第二次消防設備士、語言治療師", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02888', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-098-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '除符合「各類場所消防安全設備設置標準」第19條第2項得免設場所之規定外，下列場所何者應設置火 警自動警報設備？', '["5層以下之建築物，供證券交易所使用，任何一層樓地板面積為300平方公尺者", "10層以下供餐廳使用，總樓地板面積為200平方公尺者", "6層以上10層以下之建築物任何一層樓地板面積為200平方公尺者", "11層以上建築物"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a64d4d092471", "answer_pdf_sha1": "465b7400ec13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098220", "c": "902", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年建築師、技師、消防設備師、不動產經紀人、記帳士、第二次消防設備士、語言治療師", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02889', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-098-b8d45639', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依「各類場所消防安全設備設置標準」規定，總樓地板面積在A平方公尺以上之乙、丙、丁類場所；及 設於地下層或無開口樓層，且樓地板面積在B平方公尺以上之各類場所，應設置滅火器。其中A、B各 代表為何？', '["A=250；B=100", "A=200；B=50", "A=150；B=100", "A=150；B=50"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a64d4d092471", "answer_pdf_sha1": "465b7400ec13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098220", "c": "902", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "消防法規概要", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年建築師、技師、消防設備師、不動產經紀人、記帳士、第二次消防設備士、語言治療師", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL)
